<p>
	Panopto is expanding very rapidly and is growing its sales force accordingly. We seek highly motivated and experienced sales professionals to help drive our position in the corporate markets. Panopto&#39;s &quot;Sales Consultant&quot; is focused primarily on new customer acquisition and growing usage with existing customers. Typical sales are &quot;enterprise&quot; and require door opening and closing capabilities at the VP and C-levels.</p>
