	Experience and/or strong interest in video, search, and digital multi-media is an added plus.<br />
	Ability to work well individually, and as part of a team and culture that is passionate, driven, opportunistic, and motivated to bring meaningful and productive change to our customers.<br />
	Experience selling to the largest Seattle and West Coast companies a definite plus.<br />
	Position Requirements:</p>
<p>
	Full time position requiring strong work intensity.<br />
	Bachelors Degree.<br />
	Proficient computer skills and ability to learn and utilize new software/hardware.<br />
