o the development of Panopto EU.</p><p>Essential attributes:</p><p>Educated to degree level with at least three years&rsquo; sales experience<br />Experience in software or a related industry<br />Well organised<br />Team player with excellent presentation and communication skills<br />Excited by the possibilities and benefits of Panopto&rsquo;s award-winning technology and able to contribute to the company&rsquo;s overall development<br />Salary</p><p>An attractive basic salary plus substantial bonus is available to the right people.</p>]]></description>
